data.description: Fantastic Fairhope location just a golf cart ride into downtown! This cute cottage has everything you could need. The sqft listed does NOT include an additional 11x14 sunroom that has a split cooling system, it is right off the main living area and overlooking the private backyard.  The home is situated on a cul de sac street with a carport, private backyard with fruit trees, storage shed, separate 1 bed/1 bath with kitchenette mother in law suite/artist cottage/rental (whatever you want) approximately 500 sqft +/-. Inside the main home you will find a tastefully updated interior with beautiful quartz countertops in the kitchen, a walk in shower in the primary bath, electric fireplace in the living room, laminate hardwood flooring, ample storage, lots of light and more. Call your favorite REALTOR® to make an appointment to view today.
